OL,3,CHang glider in hospital after crash in
OL,4,CScottish Borders
OL,6,FA hang glider has been taken to
OL,7,Fhospital following a crash in the
OL,8,FScottish Borders.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,11,FInnerleithen area on Friday evening.
OL,13,FA Police Scotland spokesperson said:
OL,14,F"Around 8.35pm on Friday, 22 August,
OL,15,F2025, we received a report of a crash
OL,16,Finvolving a hand glider in the
OL,17,FInnerleithen area.
OL,19,F"Mountain Rescue attended to assist
OL,20,Fand the pilot was taken to the Royal
OL,21,FInfirmary of Edinburgh."
